
//In un direted graph 
//to find a circle.

DFS()

Explore(z)
  for neighbors w of z:
  if w not visited....
  
  if w already visited, and w is not direct parent of z, 
      then there is a cycle
      
      
      

//In direted graph 
//to find a circle.

DFS()
  create a array to reord path onStack[] =false
Explore(z)
  onStack[z]=true.
  for neighbors w of z:
  if w not visited....
  
  if w already visited, and onStack[w] = true, 
      then there is a cycle
      
  onStack[z]=false //set to false, before quit Explore.
